應該會死晒? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fff05133767fef83daad46eeaa45c41f18a6d37","tid":538694,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709984da40d8c2fa7280cce280ecc60fcf3d83f5","tid":538694,"uid":126102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"依單嘢好撚不知所謂 明明錯喺條友到 做繁殖場搵錢 但啲人就話佢有愛心識養 唔應該拉佢 屌你老味有無咁本末倒置呀？"},{"pid":"3db4fceb0c5f2f4cdd85107667d8772ad9f732ee","tid":538694,"uid":30788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"比魚龍署隨時養死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d25326fb21a8e218627189b6b6e317838e9bff","tid":538694,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依單嘢好撚不知所謂 明明錯喺條友到 做繁殖場搵錢 但啲人就話佢有愛心識養 唔應該拉佢 屌你老味有無咁本末倒置呀？</blockquote><br />\n如果唔洗牌都養得的話<br />\n我諗唔洗十年就絕種"},{"pid":"2072bf9133ae6bae8509172c3b20ad9b0e1f4cd3","tid":538694,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"香港地乜都唔養得<br />\n如果佢啲動物有得攞牌你估佢唔想apply咩？<br />\n繁殖稀有物種有技術有良心根本唔係壞事<br />\n可以肯定嘅係，漁農班友一定好快養死晒啲動物"},{"pid":"6d0fcf341b524c14e9b8fa95b0c2e50b773ca9d1","tid":538694,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"原本呢堆動物都應該長命百歲, <br />\n<br />\n依家俾漁𤐰處 捉晒, 好快就淫道痿滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7fafe92c74d4e308173922d6be3977c7d38a09","tid":538694,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"bf25f8585bf67454e469bf0cd72a4694d721fda0","tid":538694,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709984da40d8c2fa7280cce280ecc60fcf3d83f5","tid":538694,"uid":126102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"依單嘢好撚不知所謂 明明錯喺條友到 做繁殖場搵錢 但啲人就話佢有愛心識養 唔應該拉佢 屌你老味有無咁本末倒置呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以好似catch me if you can咁<br />\n俾呢條友代表政府做野, 繁殖下呢d瀕危動物<br />\n雖然用黎賺錢係仆街, 但反正都係稀有物種不如繼續養"}]}